"Kua-Toa","The following opinion may be a personal opinion of an individual Kua-Toa or it may be a more accurate restatement of the general Kua-Toa position.  I am not sure, Alex would have to say.

Marshall Macluhn would have been a Kua-Toa.  The whole point is that the medium is the message.  The problem with the ""Pulled By The Wave"" school is that they confuse this with the medium determines the message.  This flies in the face of the fundamental tenants of Kua-Toa philosophy.  I sing now to my core teachings.  The song that is at the heart of the Kua-Toa way is to facilitate and strengthen the communication between individual context generating beings (I use the term CGBs under duress since it is pale and shallow but it will be more meaningful to those hearing this song).  I support the viewpoint of an objective reality with consistent and persistent flavor to the faces we present to each other.  I am a strong proponent that when to honoured individuals interact the face that each perceives is the face that the other is communicating.  Without this basic premise there is not chaos, there is isolation.  This is the trap of the subjective reality.  The pulled by the wave school twists this into some distorted view of deterministic psychology.  they hear discussion that the face we present from encounter to encounter should be consistent and they warp this into a worldview that says that the only voice we have is determined by our environment.  In essence they do not support an objective environment for our individual souls, they negate the existence of our souls.  I give them the turbulence of my tail flukes.  The presence of an objective medium through which the noble and graceful souls which is all that we are at our cores can communicate does NOT require that the messages that we pass be limited in any way.  Remember our roots.  We are created to make a world in which consensus empowers us to act as a group.  It is a vice, a drug to become swayed by the reality that we are creating.  Reality is a tool, it is not actually so.  No matter what vehicle you use for communication there are still only souls swimming in the great beyond, no one has ever tried to deny this (except the insane and the farte addicts).  Do not confuse me with the dreamers, I do not go there.  There is a huge distinction between honouring the soul and ripping away the very fabric that allows us to communicate.  The dreamers live in a world of isolation.  There dream existence would have that the face we see in others is a creation of our own internal process.  That the messages we send between each other cannot hold content becuase there form is completely subjective in the eye of the beholder and can change on a whim.  There way leads to a fragmented ocean in which each soul lives in a world of its own creation and can no longer meaningfully interact with any other.  This is not to say that change only occurs in dream.  Change occurs in every moment in the world between us but the difference is that it is a change that is recognized and consistent between the sender of a message and its receiver.  I may be smaller than a gek in one moment and larger than the biggest Vann in the next but that is fine becuase all of the brothers who I interact with will hear they same thing that I am saying about myself.  Causality is a fine thing but it is just a decoration, an arguing point.  Consensus is the meat of our philosophy.  Do not confuse the message with the world.  Do not confuse yourself with the story you are telling.  This path only leads to suffering.

As a note, some on the council might believe that this sort of attitude was instilled in me by my long association with Mahataralani (Kisses Deep Waters) but I tell you that this view is older than any other in our race and has been my passion since my first incarnation.  Most likely this is what attracted her to me in the first place.  In any case the dream kernal that lives within me now happened far far later in the new temporal way of reckoning than this conversation.  I only hope that in the end it is a strong conversation and those who are pulled by the wave do not drag us all down with them.

    Olactalan-Tlovanu
    (Crests the waves to jump at the moon)


