"RE: Sigmund Repair","Restore to Pattern is NOT a healing spell to use on sentient beings!

Restoration is limited to the depth of pattern perceived by the spell,
which is usually less than that of the caster.  Victims of this spell
eventually become simple expressions of their former pattern, the
magical equivalent of toons.

Eman is STRONGLY against this use of the spell!


